  "body": "<!--\r\nNeed help?\r\nRefer to our contributing guidelines for additional information about making a good issue:\r\nhttps://github.com/ethereum-optimism/.github/blob/master/CONTRIBUTING.md\r\n-->\r\n\r\n**Is your feature request related to a problem? Please describe.**\r\nRight now, estimateGas can return under 21000 if the \"feeInGwei\" is less than 21000 gwei. However, Metamask prevents sending transactions with a gasLimit of under 21000. \r\n\r\n**Describe the solution you'd like**\r\nA potential hack here is for `estimateGas` to return the `Max(21000, estimateGas(tx))`\r\n\r\n**Describe alternatives you've considered**\r\nReally, we need to look into alternatives, as it appears the downstream effects of this hack will be very numerous.",
